        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="文档定义"><a href="#文档定义" class="headerlink" title="文档定义"></a>文档定义</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unsigned char _crol_ (</span><br><span class="line">  unsigned char c,        /* character to rotate left */</span><br><span class="line">  unsigned char b);       /* bit positions to rotate */</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>_crol_函数功能：将 c 进行b位左位移，并将值以unsigned char类型返回<br>_cror_函数<br>与_crol_函数类似，区别只是进行的是右位移</p><p>所属库：intrins.h   more info :<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/The_RedMaple/article/details/111424886">DSDN</a></p><h2 id="Led流水灯"><a href="#Led流水灯" class="headerlink" title="Led流水灯"></a>Led流水灯</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void <span class="function"><span class="title">Led_flow</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">P1 = Led;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(Flag == 1)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Led = _crol_(Led,1);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="按键读取函数"><a href="#按键读取函数" class="headerlink" title="按键读取函数"></a>按键读取函数</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unsigned char <span class="function"><span class="title">Key_Read</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">unsigned char temp = 0;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(P3_4 == 0) temp = 1;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(P3_5 == 0) temp = 2;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(P3_6 == 0) temp = 3;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(P3_7 == 0) temp = 4;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="按键扫描区"><a href="#按键扫描区" class="headerlink" title="按键扫描区"></a>按键扫描区</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void <span class="function"><span class="title">Key_Scan</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Key_Val = Key_Read();</span><br><span class="line">Key_Down = Key_Val &amp;(Key_Val ^ Key_Old);</span><br><span class="line">Key_Up = ~Key_Val &amp;(Key_Val ^ Key_Old);</span><br><span class="line">Key_Old = Key_Val;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="按键功能设置"><a href="#按键功能设置" class="headerlink" title="按键功能设置"></a>按键功能设置</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">void <span class="function"><span class="title">Key_Func</span></span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">switch(Key_Down)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> 1:</span><br><span class="line">Flag = 0;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> 2:</span><br><span class="line">Flag = 1;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> 3:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">case</span> 4:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
